      <h3 class="card-title">Technology</h3>
      <p class="card-subtitle">Audio production and game integration tools</p>
      <div class="tech-grid">
        <span class="tech-pill">Unity</span>
        <span class="tech-pill">FMOD</span>
        <span class="tech-pill">Wwise</span>
        <span class="tech-pill">Pro Tools</span>
        <span class="tech-pill">C#</span>
