          <span class="results-icon">🔄</span>
          <span class="results-text">Audio systems reused in team's subsequent projects</span>
        </li>
        <li class="results-item">
          <span class="results-icon">🎧</span>
          <span class="results-text">Enhanced the "headphones recommended" meditative experience</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>